    "body": "fixes #15773\r\n\r\nThe performance improvements done in #14693 where leaving the DB in an inconsistent state when specs were removed from it. This PR updates the DB internal state whenever it is written to file, but does that using a dictionary that still resides in memory to maintain the performance gain of #14693.",
